    "\n",
    "|   | Finding | Recommendation | Expected Impact |\n",
    "|---|---------|---------------|-----------------|\n",
    "| 1 | Q4 (Nov–Dec) drives ~45% of annual revenue | Pre-stock inventory by August; launch campaigns by September | Maximise peak-season revenue; prevent stockouts |\n",
    "| 2 | Champions segment drives highest revenue contribution | Implement VIP retention programme (early access, exclusive offers) | Protect high-value customers and stabilise revenue |\n",
